{"tid":1824320,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"介紹一隻屌打DIABLO既GAME","createTime":"2020-01-14T10:46:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T13:09:52.000Z","uid":139750,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef3ad657abe2dd812df09870edac91484c35b27","tid":1824320,"uid":139750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:46:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8lXwkQsHdjE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8lXwkQsHdjE&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=0a68c34b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8lXwkQsHdjE</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"438d446ca6ae4d117447758ea2f46cde5f2e6db0","tid":1824320,"uid":231016,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:47:46.000Z","msg":"騰訊不了"},{"pid":"81fd7c65ebae97403d9a9ebcf35c2ad7965d6ac5","tid":1824320,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T10:48:15.000Z","msg":"支那企鵝 不了"},{"pid":"f0fa6bb14feae7e29a7dea928cfe7d69a84f7280","tid":1824320,"uid":139750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:15:09.000Z","msg":"但我相信GGG可以出淤泥而不染<br />\n<br />\nGGG是否成騰訊的一部分？<br />\nGrinding Gear Games仍然是新西蘭獨立運營的公司。所有的開發人員仍然在為GGG工作，並沒有成騰訊的員工。創始人（克裏斯，喬納森和埃裏克）仍在經營公司，就像我們過去11年一樣。展望未來，我們僅僅只需向騰訊提供財務報告，這對我們的理念和運營只能產生最小的影響。<br />\n<br />\n騰訊是否會嘗試改變流放之路？<br />\n不是。我們與騰訊投資的其他公司的首席執行官進行了會談，並確信騰訊從未試圖幹擾中國以外的遊戲設計或運營。我們保留對流亡之路的完全控制權，並且對我們認為最適合遊戲的更改進行修改。<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/Co.php?bsn=18966&amp;sn=455216\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FCo.php%3Fbsn%3D18966%26sn%3D455216&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=c0d7b3db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/Co.php?bsn=18966&amp;sn=455216</a><br />\n<br />\n- Chris跟Rory都不會去看MTX的銷售報告. Chris認為只要把遊戲做好, 錢自然會入帳. 他知道身為CEO說 &ldquo;GGG不在乎他們賺多少錢&rdquo;是個糟糕的主意, 但大多數的GGG員工都只是想要把遊戲做到好. 當要做出公司層面上的決定時, 他不怎麼會去看金錢上會帶來什麼, 更重要的是 &ldquo;這對POE好嗎?&rdquo; &ldquo;玩家會喜歡這個MTX嗎&rdquo; &ldquo;這個會破壞我們遊戲美術的風格嗎?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n- 呈上, 的確, 當騰訊派的董事會人看到這次的訪談然後說&ldquo;欸, 你認真的?&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=18966&amp;snA=122737\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D18966%26snA%3D122737&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerqnpKMFcuJZ7CRl7dpp3bCg%3D&h=feb8e65a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=18966&amp;snA=122737</a>"},{"pid":"085bafa62d783f13288a8ec5da46708d635ffc1d","tid":1824320,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"仲垃圾過diablo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd6f8fc6c347aba5f6abf3634199ac04ff4998d2","tid":1824320,"uid":139750,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"085bafa62d783f13288a8ec5da46708d635ffc1d","tid":1824320,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"仲垃圾過diablo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T13:09:52.000Z","msg":"唔係嫁,POE個天賦樹好有特色嫁"}]}